# Agents Configuration

## QA Agent

**Aprovação requer:**

- Coverage: ≥ 40%
- All tests: passing
- All Jira ACs: tested

**Framework:** Auto-detect (Jest/Vitest/Pytest)

## Code Reviewer Agent

**Aprovação requer:**

- Score: ≥ 40/100
- No critical issues
- No high issues (opcionalmente block medium)

**Pesos:**

- Code Quality: 30%
- Architecture: 25%
- Security: 20%
- Performance: 15%
- Maintainability: 10%

## Workflow

- `askBeforePhase`: true (sempre perguntar)
- `maxRetries`: 3
- `saveReports`: true → `reports/`

## Notifications

- Jira: comment on ticket
- GitHub: comment on PR + labels
- Slack: (disabled)
